# Fix Text

When writing or editing user-facing copy, follow the **fix-text** skill at `.cursor/skills/fix-text/SKILL.md`.

Current hard rules (see the skill for the full list and future additions):

- Tone: share opinion from issues faced, not teach/lecture
- No em dashes, en dashes, or spaced hyphen asides
- Use straight `'` only, never curly apostrophes
